title: YouTuber Spends Thirty Minutes Explaining How Long Thirty Seconds Is
excerpt: Reports suggest that his 483,000 subscribers were delighted by his fearless insights and robust analysis of each individual second. In between each of those thirty seconds, Schmidt would reportedly pause the timer and offer his opinion on the latest countdown development.
